A topic and discussion I come across with people looking for #insurance is they say the same thing, "well #statefarm is more pricey than everyone else." At times yes that's true, but do you know what you are getting for when you get insurance from us?  Over 92% of insurance customers don't know what coverages they have, they don't know the difference between replacement cost and actual cash value.  Many companies pay actual cash value, except us!  To make it more simple, we are the #rollsroyce #bentley #maybach of insurance.  We give you quality, we are not here for quantity!  Give me a call, no pressure to purchase a product, I would love to educate you about coverages, the ins and outs and the value you are paying for insurance.  #texas #houston #galveston #cypresstexas #harriscounty #elpaso #sanantonio #dallas #austin #trustme
